{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The ID of the company for which the attributes and translations apply.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard\f0 The\f0  name or\f0  description of the company displayed in the \b Company\b0  field. You cannot change the description in this field.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The Logical Unit that owns the attributes.\par
}

}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The current translation related to the language code. This translation can be modified by the end user.\par
}

}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The database code or ID for the language.\par
}

{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252{\fonttbl{\f0}}\fs20\pard The full description of the language to be used. The language is displayed automatically when the language code is entered.\par
}

}

}
